ation. So, to all the women out there eyeing a career in fire protection, Viking Fire Protection is not just cheering you on; we&#8217;re inviting you to join us on this exciting journey!<\/p>\n<p>We firmly believe in equal opportunities, training, and support for anyone interested in building a rewarding career in fire protection. If you&#8217;re a woman eager to make a mark in a traditionally male-dominated industry, we invite you to explore the exciting world of fire sprinkler trade with Viking Fire Protection.<\/p>\n<p>Join us, and let&#8217;s collectively make the fire protection industry brighter, safer, and more inclusive for everyone.<\/p>\n<p>Are you ready to break barriers and unleash your potential? <a href=\"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/contact-us\/\">Reach out to us<\/a> today and explore the possibilities of a fulfilling career in fire protection. Together, let&#8217;s redefine the future of the Canadian fire sprinkler industry!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Women&#8217;s Impact on Safety, Innovation, and Inclusivity At Viking Fire Protection, our mission extends beyond saving lives; we&#8217;re committed to breaking barriers and fostering diversity within the fire protection industry. In the latest edition of CASA Notes, the spotlight shines brightly on the incredible women reshaping the landscape of the fire sprinkler trade. We take [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":8059,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1547","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-news","cf"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1547","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":